  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5291665">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5291665/" class="title-link">亚当 斯密与马克思的再读</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5291665"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/36603582/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/36603582/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">七七</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2012-02-03"
      class="main-meta">2012-02-03 21:56:24</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5291665_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  有些书，能让你学到新知识，是好书；有些书，能够激发你更多的学习欲望，亦是好书。《资本主义精神和社会主义改革》就是后者。 看完全书，作者的主旨是要阐述现存所有社会的历史都是通过提高民主和法治水平来遏制腐败的阶级斗争史。资产阶级之所以没有像马克思《资本论》中所预...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/5291665/#comments">(6回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">10有用 / 4没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_5291665_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_5291665_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



