        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28129961/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/28129961/" class="">第76页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/55640471/" class=" " title="知了">知了</a>
                (永远年轻,永远热泪盈眶)
              
                <span class="allstar40" title="推荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="28129961">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">现存所有社会的历史都是通过提高民主和法治水平来遏制腐败的阶级斗争史。
</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-08-16 20:08</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                现存所有社会的历史都是通过提高民主和法治水平来遏制腐败的阶级斗争史。

                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

